<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('./partials/head') %>
        <title>About - Suyog Sable</title>
        <style>
            body {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
                background-color: #121212;
                color: #f0f0f0;
            }

            .about-wrapper {
                max-width: 900px;
                margin: 60px auto;
                padding: 0 20px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .about-wrapper img {
                width: 140px;
                height: 140px;
                border-radius: 50%;
                object-fit: cover;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                border: 3px solid #2c2c2c;
            }

            .about-wrapper h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                font-weight: 700;
            }

            .about-wrapper h4 {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                margin: 10px 0 30px;
                color: #bbbbbb;
            }

            .about-wrapper p {
                font-size: 1rem;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #ccc;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .btn-group {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                gap: 12px;
                margin-top: 20px;
            }

            .btn-group a {
                text-decoration: none;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                background-color: #007bff;
                border-radius: 8px;
                color: #fff;
                font-weight: 500;
                transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            }

            .btn-group a:hover {
                background-color: #0056b3;
                transform: translateY(-2px);
            }

            @media (max-width: 600px) {
                .about-wrapper h1 {
                    font-size: 2rem;
                }

                .about-wrapper img {
                    width: 100px;
                    height: 100px;
                }
            }
        </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('./partials/navbar') %>

        <div class="about-wrapper">
            <img src="images/suyog.jpeg" alt="Suyog Sable">
            <h1>Suyog Sable</h1>
            <h4>Engineer • Developer • Problem-solver</h4>
            <p>
                Hi, I’m Suyog — a passionate full-stack developer, tech enthusiast, and problem-solver. I love working
                on real-world projects involving AI, web development, and innovative systems. My goal is to build
                meaningful tech that helps people and improves everyday life.
            </p>
            <p>
                I’ve built apps like an Inventory Tracker with AI forecasting, a CRM System , and
                multiple full-stack platforms using Node.js, MongoDB, and React. Always curious, always learning.
            </p>
            <div class="btn-group">
                <a href="https://github.com/Suyog-Sable" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/suyog-sable/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
                <a href="mailto:suyogsable3@gmail.com">Email Me</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('partials/script') %>
</body>

</html>